lead_paragraph: The Sports of The Times column on Friday, about the potential impact of changes to the women’s tennis calendar on Serena and Venus Williams, misspelled the given name of a player Serena Williams defeated at the Sony Ericsson Open and misstated the day of their match. She is Justine Henin, not Justin; the match was last Tuesday — not Monday, March 31.
